#. <section class="sutta" id="dn12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "dn12:0.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Long Discourses 12"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn12:0.2"
msgid "Lohiccasutta"
msgstr "With Lohicca"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.224"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "dn12:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena "
"saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi yena sālavatikā tadavasari."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Kosalans together "
"with a large Saṅgha of five hundred mendicants when he arrived at Sālavatikā."

msgctxt "dn12:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati sattussadaṃ "
"satiṇakaṭṭhodakaṃ sadhaññaṃ rājabhoggaṃ raññā pasenadinā kosalena dinnaṃ "
"rājadāyaṃ brahmadeyyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the brahmin Lohicca was living in Sālavatikā. It was a "
"crown property given by King Pasenadi of Kosala, teeming with living "
"creatures, full of hay, wood, water, and grain, a royal endowment of the "
"highest quality."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ "
"uppannaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "Now at that time Lohicca had the following harmful misconception:"

msgctxt "dn12:2.2"
msgid ""
"“idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati."
msgstr ""
"“Should an ascetic or brahmin achieve some skillful quality, they ought not "
"inform anyone else. For what can one person do for another?"

msgctxt "dn12:2.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr "Suppose someone cut off an old bond, only to create another new bond."

msgctxt "dn12:2.4"
msgid ""
"evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi, kiñhi paro parassa "
"karissatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. For what can "
"one person do for another?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.225"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:3.1"
msgid "Assosi kho lohicco brāhmaṇo:"
msgstr "Lohicca heard:"

msgctxt "dn12:3.2"
msgid ""
"“samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ "
"caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi "
"sālavatikaṃ anuppatto."
msgstr ""
"“It seems the ascetic Gotama—a Sakyan, gone forth from a Sakyan family—has "
"arrived at Sālavatikā, together with a large Saṅgha of five hundred "
"mendicants."

msgctxt "dn12:3.3"
msgid "Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato:"
msgstr "He has this good reputation:"

msgctxt "dn12:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū "
"anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "dn12:3.5"
msgid ""
"So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ "
"sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti."
msgstr ""
"He has realized with his own insight this world—with its gods, Māras and "
"Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, gods and humans—and "
"he makes it known to others."

msgctxt "dn12:3.6"
msgid ""
"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ "
"sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti."
msgstr ""
"He teaches Dhamma that’s good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good "
"in the end, meaningful and well-phrased. And he reveals a spiritual practice "
"that’s entirely full and pure."

msgctxt "dn12:3.7"
msgid "Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī”ti."
msgstr "It’s good to see such perfected ones.”"

# While nhapita would seem to be identical with nhapaka, i.e bathroom attendant, it is translated by all as barber. This must follow Ja 395, where it explicitly means barber.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: rosikaṃ → bhesikaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "dn12:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo rosikaṃ nhāpitaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then Lohicca addressed his barber Rosika:"

msgctxt "dn12:4.2"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, samma rosike, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā "
"mama vacanena samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ "
"phāsuvihāraṃ puccha:"
msgstr ""
"“Here, dear Rosika, go to the ascetic Gotama and in my name bow with your "
"head to his feet. Ask him if he is healthy and well, nimble, strong, and "
"living comfortably."

msgctxt "dn12:4.3"
msgid ""
"‘lohicco, bho gotama, brāhmaṇo bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ "
"lahuṭṭhānaṃ balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchatī’ti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:4.4"
msgid "evañca vadehi—"
msgstr "And then ask him whether he,"

# Note the unusual use of kira in this idiom, shared with MN 85 and MN 127. I think this expresses an extra degree of polite deference, and render with “might” rather than “would”.
msgctxt "dn12:4.5"
msgid ""
"adhivāsetu kira bhavaṃ gotamo lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ "
"saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṃghenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"together with the mendicant Saṅgha, might accept tomorrow’s meal from the "
"brahmin Lohicca.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: Evaṃ, bho”ti → evaṃ bhanteti (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "dn12:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho rosikā nhāpito lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena "
"bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ "
"nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Rosika replied. He did as he was asked, and"

msgctxt "dn12:5.2"
msgid ""
"“lohicco, bhante, brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ "
"balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:5.3"
msgid "evañca vadeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:5.4"
msgid ""
"adhivāsetu kira, bhante, bhagavā lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ "
"saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṃghenā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:5.5"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr "the Buddha consented in silence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs6"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.226"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: rosikā → bhesikā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "dn12:6.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā yena lohicco brāhmaṇo "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then, knowing that the Buddha had accepted, Rosika got up from his seat, "
"went to Lohicca, and said to him:"

#. VAR: mayaṃ bhoto → mayaṃ bhante tava (bj, pts1)
#. VAR: avocumhā kho → avocumha bho (pts1)
msgctxt "dn12:6.2"
msgid "“avocumhā kho mayaṃ bhoto vacanena taṃ bhagavantaṃ:"
msgstr "“I gave the Buddha your message,"

msgctxt "dn12:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘lohicco, bhante, brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ appābādhaṃ appātaṅkaṃ lahuṭṭhānaṃ "
"balaṃ phāsuvihāraṃ pucchati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:6.4"
msgid "evañca vadeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:6.5"
msgid ""
"adhivāsetu kira, bhante, bhagavā lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa svātanāya bhattaṃ "
"saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṃghenā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:6.6"
msgid "Adhivutthañca pana tena bhagavatā”ti."
msgstr "and he accepted.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo tassā rattiyā accayena sake nivesane paṇītaṃ "
"khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā rosikaṃ nhāpitaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"And when the night had passed Lohicca had a variety of delicious foods "
"prepared in his own home. Then he had the Buddha informed of the time, "
"saying:"

msgctxt "dn12:7.2"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, samma rosike, yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā "
"samaṇassa gotamassa kālaṃ ārocehi—"
msgstr ""
"“Here, dear Rosika, go to the ascetic Gotama and announce the time, saying:"

msgctxt "dn12:7.3"
msgid "kālo, bho gotama, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti."
msgstr "‘Itʼs time, Master Gotama, the meal is ready.’”"

msgctxt "dn12:7.4"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bho”ti kho rosikā nhāpito lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa paṭissutvā yena "
"bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ "
"aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Rosika replied. He did as he was asked."

msgctxt "dn12:7.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavato kālaṃ ārocesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:7.6"
msgid "“kālo, bhante, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:7.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya saddhiṃ "
"bhikkhusaṅghena yena sālavatikā tenupasaṅkami."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, went "
"to Sālavatikā together with the Saṅgha of mendicants."

#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs8"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:8.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito "
"anubandho hoti."
msgstr "Now, Rosika was following behind the Buddha,"

msgctxt "dn12:8.2"
msgid "Atha kho rosikā nhāpito bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and told him of Lohicca’s views, adding:"

msgctxt "dn12:8.3"
msgid "“lohiccassa, bhante, brāhmaṇassa evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.4"
msgid ""
"‘idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.5"
msgid "kiñhi paro parassa karissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.7"
msgid "evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.8"
msgid "kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:8.9"
msgid ""
"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etasmā pāpakā diṭṭhigatā "
"vivecetū”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, please dissuade him from that harmful misconception.”"

msgctxt "dn12:8.10"
msgid "“Appeva nāma siyā, rosike, appeva nāma siyā, rosike”ti."
msgstr "“Hopefully that’ll happen, Rosika, hopefully that’ll happen.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs9"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.227"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:9.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā yena lohiccassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha approached Lohicca’s home, where he sat on the seat spread "
"out."

msgctxt "dn12:9.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena "
"khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi."
msgstr ""
"Then Lohicca served and satisfied the mendicant Saṅgha headed by the Buddha "
"with his own hands with a variety of delicious foods."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn12:9.3"
msgid "1. Lohiccabrāhmaṇānuyoga"
msgstr "1. Questioning Lohicca"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:9.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho lohicco brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ "
"nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha had eaten and washed his hand and bowl, Lohicca took a low "
"seat and sat to one side."

msgctxt "dn12:9.5"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho lohiccaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "dn12:9.6"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira te, lohicca, evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Is it really true, Lohicca, that you have such a harmful misconception:"

msgctxt "dn12:9.7"
msgid ""
"‘idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati."
msgstr ""
"‘Should an ascetic or brahmin achieve some skillful quality, they ought not "
"inform anyone else. For what can one person do for another?"

msgctxt "dn12:9.8"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr "Suppose someone cut off an old bond, only to create another new bond."

msgctxt "dn12:9.9"
msgid ""
"evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi, kiñhi paro parassa "
"karissatī’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. For what can "
"one person do for another?’”"

msgctxt "dn12:9.10"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Yes, Master Gotama.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs10"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:10.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, lohicca, "
msgstr "“What do you think, Lohicca? "

msgctxt "dn12:10.2"
msgid "nanu tvaṃ sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasasī”ti?"
msgstr "Do you reside in Sālavatikā?”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Yes, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.4"
msgid "“Yo nu kho, lohicca, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "“Lohicca, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "dn12:10.5"
msgid "‘lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr "‘The brahmin Lohicca reigns over Sālavatikā."

msgctxt "dn12:10.6"
msgid ""
"Yā sālavatikāya samudayasañjāti lohiccova taṃ brāhmaṇo ekako paribhuñjeyya, "
"na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"He alone should enjoy the revenues produced in Sālavatikā and not share them "
"with anyone else.’"

msgctxt "dn12:10.7"
msgid "Evaṃ vādī so ye taṃ upajīvanti, tesaṃ antarāyakaro vā hoti, no vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Would the person who spoke like that make it difficult for those whose "
"living depends on you or not?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:10.8"
msgid "“Antarāyakaro, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“They would, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.9"
msgid "“Antarāyakaro samāno hitānukampī vā tesaṃ hoti ahitānukampī vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But is someone who creates difficulties for others acting kindly or "
"unkindly?”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.10"
msgid "“Ahitānukampī, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Unkindly, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.11"
msgid ""
"“Ahitānukampissa mettaṃ vā tesu cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sapattakaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But does an unkind person have love in their heart or hostility?”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.12"
msgid "“Sapattakaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Hostility, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.13"
msgid "“Sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi vā hoti sammādiṭṭhi vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“And when the heart is full of hostility, is there right view or wrong view?”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.14"
msgid "“Micchādiṭṭhi, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Wrong view, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:10.15"
msgid ""
"“Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "“An individual with wrong view is reborn in one of two places, I say:"

msgctxt "dn12:10.16"
msgid "nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā."
msgstr "hell or the animal realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:11.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, lohicca,"
msgstr "What do you think, Lohicca?"

msgctxt "dn12:11.2"
msgid "nanu rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasatī”ti?"
msgstr "Does King Pasenadi reign over Kāsī and Kosala?”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Yes, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.4"
msgid "“Yo nu kho, lohicca, evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "“Lohicca, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "dn12:11.5"
msgid "‘rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasati;"
msgstr "‘King Pasenadi reigns over Kāsī and Kosala."

msgctxt "dn12:11.6"
msgid ""
"yā kāsikosale samudayasañjāti, rājāva taṃ pasenadi kosalo ekako "
"paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"He alone should enjoy the revenues produced in Kāsī and Kosala and not share "
"them with anyone else.’"

msgctxt "dn12:11.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vādī so ye rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ upajīvanti tumhe ceva aññe ca, "
"tesaṃ antarāyakaro vā hoti, no vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Would the person who spoke like that make it difficult for yourself and "
"others whose living depends on King Pasenadi or not?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.228"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:11.8"
msgid "“Antarāyakaro, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“They would, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.9"
msgid "“Antarāyakaro samāno hitānukampī vā tesaṃ hoti ahitānukampī vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But is someone who creates difficulties for others acting kindly or "
"unkindly?”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.10"
msgid "“Ahitānukampī, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Unkindly, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.11"
msgid ""
"“Ahitānukampissa mettaṃ vā tesu cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti sapattakaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But does an unkind person have love in their heart or hostility?”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.12"
msgid "“Sapattakaṃ, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Hostility, sir.”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.13"
msgid "“Sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi vā hoti sammādiṭṭhi vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“And when the heart is full of hostility, is there right view or wrong view?”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.14"
msgid "“Micchādiṭṭhi, bho gotama”."
msgstr "“Wrong view, Master Gotama.”"

msgctxt "dn12:11.15"
msgid ""
"“Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "“An individual with wrong view is reborn in one of two places, I say:"

msgctxt "dn12:11.16"
msgid "nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā."
msgstr "hell or the animal realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:12.1"
msgid "Iti kira, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""
"So it seems, Lohicca, that should someone say such a thing either of Lohicca "
"or of King Pasenadi,"

msgctxt "dn12:12.2"
msgid "‘lohicco brāhmaṇo sālavatikaṃ ajjhāvasati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:12.3"
msgid ""
"yā sālavatikāya samudayasañjāti, lohiccova taṃ brāhmaṇo ekako paribhuñjeyya, "
"na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs13"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:13.1"
msgid "Evaṃvādī so ye taṃ upajīvanti, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:13.2"
msgid ""
"Antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ "
"paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr "that is wrong view."

msgctxt "dn12:13.3"
msgid "Evameva kho, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "In the same way, suppose someone were to say:"

msgctxt "dn12:13.4"
msgid ""
"‘idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati."
msgstr ""
"‘Should an ascetic or brahmin achieve some skillful quality, they ought not "
"inform anyone else. For what can one person do for another?"

msgctxt "dn12:13.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya … "
"pe …"
msgstr "Suppose someone cut off an old bond, only to create another new bond."

msgctxt "dn12:13.6"
msgid "karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. For what can "
"one person do for another?’"

msgctxt "dn12:13.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃvādī so ye te kulaputtā tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ āgamma "
"evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchanti, sotāpattiphalampi sacchikaronti, "
"sakadāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, anāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, arahattampi "
"sacchikaronti, ye cime dibbā gabbhā paripācenti dibbānaṃ bhavānaṃ "
"abhinibbattiyā, tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti, antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī "
"hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte "
"paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, there are respectable persons who, relying on the teaching and training "
"proclaimed by the Realized One, achieve a high distinction such as the "
"following: they realize the fruit of stream-entry, the fruit of once-return, "
"the fruit of non-return, or the fruit of perfection. And in addition, there "
"are those who ripen the seeds for rebirth in a heavenly state. The person "
"who spoke like that makes it difficult for them. They’re acting unkindly, "
"their heart is full of hostility, and they have wrong view."

msgctxt "dn12:13.8"
msgid ""
"Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr "An individual with wrong view is reborn in one of two places, I say:"

msgctxt "dn12:13.9"
msgid "nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā."
msgstr "hell or the animal realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.229"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:14.1"
msgid "Iti kira, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:14.2"
msgid "‘rājā pasenadi kosalo kāsikosalaṃ ajjhāvasati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:14.3"
msgid ""
"yā kāsikosale samudayasañjāti, rājāva taṃ pasenadi kosalo ekako "
"paribhuñjeyya, na aññesaṃ dadeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs15"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:15.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃvādī so ye rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ upajīvanti tumhe ceva aññe ca, "
"tesaṃ antarāyakaro hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.2"
msgid ""
"Antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ "
"paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.3"
msgid "Evameva kho, lohicca, yo evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.4"
msgid ""
"‘idha samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigaccheyya, kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"adhigantvā na parassa āroceyya, kiñhi paro parassa karissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi nāma … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.6"
msgid "kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.7"
msgid ""
"Evaṃvādī so ye te kulaputtā tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ āgamma "
"evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchanti, sotāpattiphalampi sacchikaronti, "
"sakadāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, anāgāmiphalampi sacchikaronti, arahattampi "
"sacchikaronti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.8"
msgid ""
"Ye cime dibbā gabbhā paripācenti dibbānaṃ bhavānaṃ abhinibbattiyā, tesaṃ "
"antarāyakaro hoti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.9"
msgid ""
"antarāyakaro samāno ahitānukampī hoti, ahitānukampissa sapattakaṃ cittaṃ "
"paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti, sapattake citte paccupaṭṭhite micchādiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.10"
msgid ""
"Micchādiṭṭhissa kho ahaṃ, lohicca, dvinnaṃ gatīnaṃ aññataraṃ gatiṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:15.11"
msgid "nirayaṃ vā tiracchānayoniṃ vā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn12:15.12"
msgid "2. Tayocodanārahā"
msgstr "2. Three Teachers Who Deserve to Be Reprimanded"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:16.1"
msgid "Tayo khome, lohicca, satthāro, ye loke codanārahā;"
msgstr ""
"Lohicca, there are three kinds of teachers in the world who deserve to be "
"reprimanded."

msgctxt "dn12:16.2"
msgid ""
"yo ca panevarūpe satthāro codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā anavajjā."
msgstr ""
"When someone reprimands such teachers, the reprimand is true, substantive, "
"legitimate, and blameless."

msgctxt "dn12:16.3"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "dn12:16.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, lohicca, ekacco satthā yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti, "
"svāssa sāmaññattho ananuppatto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Firstly, take a teacher who has not reached the goal of the ascetic life for "
"which they went forth from the lay life to homelessness."

msgctxt "dn12:16.5"
msgid "So taṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr "They teach their disciples:"

msgctxt "dn12:16.6"
msgid "‘idaṃ vo hitāya idaṃ vo sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is for your welfare. This is for your happiness.’"

msgctxt "dn12:16.7"
msgid ""
"Tassa sāvakā na sussūsanti, na sotaṃ odahanti, na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti, "
"vokkamma ca satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr ""
"But their disciples don’t want to listen. They don’t pay attention or apply "
"their minds to understand. They proceed having turned away from the teacher’"
"s instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:16.8"
msgid "So evamassa codetabbo:"
msgstr "That teacher deserves to be reprimanded:"

msgctxt "dn12:16.9"
msgid ""
"‘āyasmā kho yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito, so te sāmaññattho "
"ananuppatto, taṃ tvaṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desesi:"
msgstr ""
"‘Venerable, you haven’t reached the goal of the ascetic life; and when you "
"teach disciples"

msgctxt "dn12:16.10"
msgid "“idaṃ vo hitāya idaṃ vo sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:16.11"
msgid ""
"Tassa te sāvakā na sussūsanti, na sotaṃ odahanti, na aññā cittaṃ "
"upaṭṭhapenti, vokkamma ca satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr "they proceed having turned away from the teacher’s instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:16.12"
msgid "Seyyathāpi nāma osakkantiyā vā ussakkeyya, parammukhiṃ vā āliṅgeyya;"
msgstr ""
"It’s like a man who makes advances on a woman though she pulls away, or "
"embraces her though she turns her back."

msgctxt "dn12:16.13"
msgid "evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi—"
msgstr ""
"That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. For what can "
"one do for another?’"

msgctxt "dn12:16.14"
msgid "kiñhi paro parassa karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:16.15"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, lohicca, paṭhamo satthā, yo loke codanāraho;"
msgstr "This is the first kind of teacher who deserves to be reprimanded."

msgctxt "dn12:16.16"
msgid ""
"yo ca panevarūpaṃ satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā anavajjā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs17"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.231"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:17.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, lohicca, idhekacco satthā yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajito hoti, svāssa sāmaññattho ananuppatto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a teacher who has not reached the goal of the ascetic life "
"for which they went forth from the lay life to homelessness."

msgctxt "dn12:17.2"
msgid "So taṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr "They teach their disciples:"

msgctxt "dn12:17.3"
msgid "‘idaṃ vo hitāya, idaṃ vo sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is for your welfare. This is for your happiness.’"

# Note that at DN 29, the opposite formulation is samādāya taṃ dhammaṃ vattati
msgctxt "dn12:17.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa sāvakā sussūsanti, sotaṃ odahanti, aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti, na ca "
"vokkamma satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr ""
"Their disciples do want to listen. They pay attention and apply their minds "
"to understand. They don’t proceed having turned away from the teacher’s "
"instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:17.5"
msgid "So evamassa codetabbo:"
msgstr "That teacher deserves to be reprimanded:"

msgctxt "dn12:17.6"
msgid ""
"‘āyasmā kho yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito, so te sāmaññattho "
"ananuppatto. Taṃ tvaṃ sāmaññatthaṃ ananupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desesi:"
msgstr ""
"‘Venerable, you haven’t reached the goal of the ascetic life; and when you "
"teach disciples"

msgctxt "dn12:17.7"
msgid "“idaṃ vo hitāya, idaṃ vo sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:17.8"
msgid ""
"Tassa te sāvakā sussūsanti, sotaṃ odahanti, aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti, na ca "
"vokkamma satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr "they don’t proceed having turned away from the teacher’s instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:17.9"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma sakaṃ khettaṃ ohāya paraṃ khettaṃ niddāyitabbaṃ maññeyya, "
"evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi—kiñhi paro parassa "
"karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s like someone who abandons their own field and presumes to weed someone "
"else’s field. That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. "
"For what can one do for another?’"

msgctxt "dn12:17.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, lohicca, dutiyo satthā, yo, loke codanāraho;"
msgstr "This is the second kind of teacher who deserves to be reprimanded."

msgctxt "dn12:17.11"
msgid ""
"yo ca panevarūpaṃ satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā anavajjā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs18"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.232"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:18.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, lohicca, idhekacco satthā yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajito hoti, svāssa sāmaññattho anuppatto hoti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a teacher who has reached the goal of the ascetic life for "
"which they went forth from the lay life to homelessness."

msgctxt "dn12:18.2"
msgid "So taṃ sāmaññatthaṃ anupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti:"
msgstr "They teach their disciples:"

msgctxt "dn12:18.3"
msgid "‘idaṃ vo hitāya, idaṃ vo sukhāyā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is for your welfare. This is for your happiness.’"

msgctxt "dn12:18.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa sāvakā na sussūsanti, na sotaṃ odahanti, na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhapenti, "
"vokkamma ca satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr ""
"But their disciples don’t want to listen. They don’t pay attention or apply "
"their minds to understand. They proceed having turned away from the teacher’"
"s instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:18.5"
msgid "So evamassa codetabbo:"
msgstr "That teacher deserves to be reprimanded:"

msgctxt "dn12:18.6"
msgid ""
"‘āyasmā kho yassatthāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito, so te sāmaññattho "
"anuppatto."
msgstr ""
"‘Venerable, you have reached the goal of the ascetic life; yet when you "
"teach disciples"

msgctxt "dn12:18.7"
msgid "Taṃ tvaṃ sāmaññatthaṃ anupāpuṇitvā sāvakānaṃ dhammaṃ desesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:18.8"
msgid "“idaṃ vo hitāya, idaṃ vo sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:18.9"
msgid ""
"Tassa te sāvakā na sussūsanti, na sotaṃ odahanti, na aññā cittaṃ "
"upaṭṭhapenti, vokkamma ca satthusāsanā vattanti."
msgstr "they proceed having turned away from the teacher’s instruction."

msgctxt "dn12:18.10"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma purāṇaṃ bandhanaṃ chinditvā aññaṃ navaṃ bandhanaṃ kareyya;"
msgstr "Suppose someone cut off an old bond, only to create another new bond."

msgctxt "dn12:18.11"
msgid ""
"evaṃ sampadamidaṃ pāpakaṃ lobhadhammaṃ vadāmi, kiñhi paro parassa "
"karissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s the consequence of such a wicked, greedy deed, I say. For what can "
"one person do for another?’"

msgctxt "dn12:18.12"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, lohicca, tatiyo satthā, yo loke codanāraho;"
msgstr "This is the third kind of teacher who deserves to be reprimanded."

msgctxt "dn12:18.13"
msgid ""
"yo ca panevarūpaṃ satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā anavajjā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:18.14"
msgid "Ime kho, lohicca, tayo satthāro, ye loke codanārahā, "
msgstr ""
"These are the three kinds of teachers in the world who deserve to be "
"reprimanded. "

msgctxt "dn12:18.15"
msgid ""
"yo ca panevarūpe satthāro codeti, sā codanā bhūtā tacchā dhammikā "
"anavajjā”ti."
msgstr ""
"When someone reprimands such teachers, the reprimand is true, substantive, "
"legitimate, and blameless.”"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn12:18.16"
msgid "3. Nacodanārahasatthu"
msgstr "3. A Teacher Who Does Not Deserve to Be Reprimanded"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:19.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, lohicco brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Lohicca said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn12:19.2"
msgid "“atthi pana, bho gotama, koci satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But Master Gotama, is there a teacher in the world who does not deserve to "
"be reprimanded?”"

msgctxt "dn12:19.3"
msgid "“Atthi kho, lohicca, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho”ti."
msgstr "“There is, Lohicca.”"

msgctxt "dn12:19.4"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho”ti?"
msgstr "“But who is that teacher?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs20-55"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.233"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:20-55.1"
msgid "“Idha, lohicca, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ, sammāsambuddho … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“It’s when a Realized One arises in the world, perfected, a fully awakened "
"Buddha …"

msgctxt "dn12:20-55.2"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, lohicca, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti … pe …"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is accomplished in ethics. …"

msgctxt "dn12:20-55.3"
msgid "paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati …"
msgstr "They enter and remain in the first absorption …"

msgctxt "dn12:20-55.4"
msgid ""
"yasmiṃ kho, lohicca, satthari sāvako evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchati, "
"ayampi kho, lohicca, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho."
msgstr ""
"A teacher under whom a disciple achieves such a high distinction is one who "
"does not deserve to be reprimanded."

msgctxt "dn12:20-55.5"
msgid ""
"Yo ca panevarūpaṃ satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā abhūtā atacchā adhammikā "
"sāvajjā."
msgstr ""
"When someone reprimands such a teacher, the reprimand is false, baseless, "
"illegitimate, and blameworthy."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs56-62"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:56-62.1"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:56-62.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They enter and remain in the second absorption …"

msgctxt "dn12:56-62.3"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "third absorption …"

msgctxt "dn12:56-62.4"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "fourth absorption."

msgctxt "dn12:56-62.5"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ kho, lohicca, satthari sāvako evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchati, "
"ayampi kho, lohicca, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho, yo ca panevarūpaṃ "
"satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā abhūtā atacchā adhammikā sāvajjā."
msgstr ""
"A teacher under whom a disciple achieves such a high distinction is one who "
"does not deserve to be reprimanded. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs63-77"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:63-77.1"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:63-77.2"
msgid "Ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti …"
msgstr "They extend and project the mind toward knowledge and vision …"

msgctxt "dn12:63-77.3"
msgid ""
"yasmiṃ kho, lohicca, satthari sāvako evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchati, "
"ayampi kho, lohicca, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho, yo ca panevarūpaṃ "
"satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā abhūtā atacchā adhammikā sāvajjā."
msgstr ""
"A teacher under whom a disciple achieves such a high distinction is one who "
"does not deserve to be reprimanded. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.234"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:63-77.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn12:63-77.5"
msgid "Nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāti."
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’"

msgctxt "dn12:63-77.6"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ kho, lohicca, satthari sāvako evarūpaṃ uḷāraṃ visesaṃ adhigacchati, "
"ayampi kho, lohicca, satthā, yo loke nacodanāraho, yo ca panevarūpaṃ "
"satthāraṃ codeti, sā codanā abhūtā atacchā adhammikā sāvajjā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A teacher under whom a disciple achieves such a high distinction is one who "
"does not deserve to be reprimanded. When someone reprimands such a teacher, "
"the reprimand is false, baseless, illegitimate, and blameworthy.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs78"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "dn12:78.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, lohicco brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Lohicca said to the Buddha:"

# At Thag 16.8, naraka is clearly a term for a cliff in a normal sense. Better to assume a naturalistic meaning here.
msgctxt "dn12:78.2"
msgid ""
"“seyyathāpi, bho gotama, puriso purisaṃ narakapapātaṃ patantaṃ kesesu "
"gahetvā uddharitvā thale patiṭṭhapeyya;"
msgstr ""
"“Suppose, Master Gotama, a person was on the verge of falling off a cliff, "
"and another person were to grab them by the hair, pull them up, and place "
"them on firm ground."

msgctxt "dn12:78.3"
msgid ""
"evamevāhaṃ bhotā gotamena narakapapātaṃ papatanto uddharitvā thale "
"patiṭṭhāpito."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when I was falling off a cliff Master Gotama pulled me up "
"and placed me on safe ground."

msgctxt "dn12:78.4"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent!"

msgctxt "dn12:78.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""
"As if he was righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good "
"eyes can see what’s there, just so has Master Gotama made the Teaching clear "
"in many ways."

msgctxt "dn12:78.6"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant "
"Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn12:78.7"
msgid ""
"Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn12:78.8"
msgid "Lohiccasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
